{"ocr_results":[{"text":"been accused of raping his younger sister by his own mother--and sent to","box":[[117,152],[1388,154],[1388,182],[117,180]]},{"text":"labor reform.:","box":[[118,187],[388,189],[388,216],[118,214]]},{"text":"So he was not really kicked out for bad work, this was","box":[[377,188],[1336,191],[1336,218],[377,215]]},{"text":"just part of the problem.","box":[[118,225],[562,224],[562,251],[118,252]]},{"text":"He also came back to the factory after three","box":[[591,223],[1373,225],[1373,255],[591,253]]},{"text":"years.","box":[[118,265],[256,261],[256,285],[119,289]]},{"text":"Sopeople","box":[[260,263],[422,263],[422,286],[260,286]]},{"text":"egenerallyarenotfiredforbadwork.","box":[[410,263],[1110,263],[1110,286],[410,286]]},{"text":"Basically there","box":[[1120,261],[1387,264],[1387,291],[1120,288]]},{"text":"is criticism, then another criticism with a recording in your file, and","box":[[118,294],[1372,296],[1372,324],[118,322]]},{"text":"expulsion is only","box":[[120,331],[421,331],[421,355],[120,355]]},{"text":"ythelast resort.","box":[[409,331],[717,334],[717,357],[409,354]]},{"text":"All of this is not to say that there i","box":[[188,365],[853,368],[853,395],[188,392]]},{"text":"is no punishment at all.","box":[[839,368],[1263,370],[1263,393],[839,391]]},{"text":"From","box":[[1299,371],[1370,371],[1370,393],[1299,393]]},{"text":"1969-74 they had meetings","box":[[120,403],[561,403],[561,427],[120,427]]},{"text":"tocriticize people in","box":[[552,402],[970,404],[970,430],[552,428]]},{"text":"n the shops and small groups.","box":[[956,402],[1456,405],[1456,432],[956,429]]},{"text":"If there was a quality control problem in the group, they would meet the","box":[[117,437],[1389,438],[1389,466],[117,465]]},{"text":"next day and find out who was responsible.l","box":[[118,473],[905,473],[905,500],[118,500]]},{"text":"If the family","box":[[891,475],[1129,476],[1129,500],[891,499]]},{"text":"background of","box":[[1115,475],[1370,473],[1370,500],[1115,502]]},{"text":"the worker responsible was that of worker or poor peasant, then they would","box":[[120,507],[1425,509],[1425,539],[120,537]]},{"text":"criticize him and this would be","box":[[122,545],[672,545],[672,569],[122,569]]},{"text":"e considered a small problem.","box":[[659,544],[1194,547],[1193,571],[659,568]]},{"text":"But if your","box":[[1188,543],[1386,546],[1386,573],[1187,570]]},{"text":"class background was not good, they would turn this into a struggle-criticism","box":[[121,580],[1475,580],[1475,607],[121,607]]},{"text":"session.","box":[[121,616],[259,616],[259,640],[121,640]]},{"text":"They might hold an all-shop repudiation meeting where they would","box":[[297,615],[1422,615],[1422,642],[297,642]]},{"text":"all yell \"down with Wang!\" and you would have to confess to receiving orders","box":[[121,650],[1457,650],[1457,677],[121,677]]},{"text":"from your capitalist father or other relative to","box":[[121,686],[970,684],[970,711],[121,713]]},{"text":"sabotage production and","box":[[982,687],[1387,685],[1387,709],[982,711]]},{"text":"socialism.","box":[[121,722],[298,722],[298,746],[121,746]]},{"text":"Notuntil1974orsodid","box":[[328,722],[760,722],[760,745],[328,745]]},{"text":"thismethod","box":[[753,723],[968,723],[968,744],[753,744]]},{"text":"l gradually begin to taper off.","box":[[960,721],[1490,720],[1490,747],[960,748]]},{"text":"But they used it right up until l976 in Shanghai because of Chang Ch'un-ch'iao's","box":[[119,757],[1527,757],[1527,784],[119,784]]},{"text":"control there.","box":[[120,789],[366,792],[366,819],[120,816]]},{"text":"So as a result, workers and technicians were afraid to make mistakes","box":[[188,825],[1387,821],[1387,852],[188,855]]},{"text":"in quality, and were afraid to do anything in violation of the orders of","box":[[120,859],[1388,859],[1388,889],[120,889]]},{"text":"the shop leaders.","box":[[123,898],[444,898],[444,922],[123,922]]},{"text":"They were afraid to be caught in a mistake and be criti-","box":[[454,896],[1440,894],[1440,921],[454,923]]},{"text":"cized.","box":[[123,933],[261,933],[261,957],[123,957]]},{"text":"So generally people were fairly careful about the quality","box":[[257,931],[1270,929],[1270,959],[257,961]]},{"text":" of their","box":[[1260,933],[1421,933],[1421,957],[1260,957]]},{"text":"work.","box":[[121,970],[211,970],[211,991],[121,991]]},{"text":"They had no trouble meeting","box":[[241,967],[725,966],[725,993],[241,994]]},{"text":"g their quotas.","box":[[710,966],[987,967],[987,994],[710,993]]},{"text":"For example, in his shop","box":[[996,964],[1423,965],[1423,995],[996,994]]},{"text":"during 1969-72, the quotas was 300","box":[[121,1003],[725,1001],[725,1028],[121,1030]]},{"text":"s","box":[[720,1005],[747,1010],[744,1026],[717,1022]]},{"text":"sewing machine heads a day. He was","box":[[735,1002],[1336,1001],[1336,1028],[735,1029]]},{"text":"personally","box":[[120,1042],[303,1040],[303,1064],[120,1066]]},{"text":"1 capable bf doing","box":[[290,1039],[600,1039],[600,1063],[290,1063]]},{"text":"g 450 in an 8 hour shift, and could easily finish","box":[[587,1037],[1442,1036],[1442,1063],[587,1064]]},{"text":"the 300in6 hours.1","box":[[123,1075],[495,1075],[495,1098],[123,1098]]},{"text":"But he wanted tooverfulfill the quota in order to","box":[[485,1073],[1371,1071],[1371,1098],[485,1100]]},{"text":"be transfered to technical work.","box":[[119,1110],[721,1108],[721,1132],[119,1134]]},{"text":"But the average worker stayed fairly","box":[[715,1108],[1352,1107],[1352,1134],[715,1135]]},{"text":"close to the standard quota, because to overfulfill would have required a","box":[[122,1144],[1406,1144],[1406,1171],[122,1171]]},{"text":"lot of hard work.","box":[[121,1182],[418,1182],[418,1205],[121,1205]]},{"text":"An example.","box":[[190,1219],[414,1219],[414,1243],[190,1243]]},{"text":"There was a young worker, a middle school graduate, who","box":[[417,1216],[1388,1211],[1388,1241],[417,1246]]},{"text":"joined the factory in l972. His first year his work was good, but later,","box":[[119,1250],[1403,1248],[1403,1279],[119,1281]]},{"text":"after some 3-4 years as a young worker, he tried to finish his work in 4-5","box":[[118,1286],[1426,1281],[1426,1314],[118,1319]]},{"text":"hours, then would use the rest of his time to wash his clothes, do personal","box":[[119,1323],[1439,1321],[1439,1348],[119,1350]]},{"text":"thingsinthefactory.","box":[[124,1361],[546,1361],[546,1384],[124,1384]]},{"text":"Butinordertofinishearly hedidthingsagainst","box":[[541,1358],[1422,1358],[1422,1381],[541,1381]]},{"text":"established tooling procedures and this resulted in violation of quality","box":[[119,1392],[1388,1389],[1388,1419],[119,1422]]},{"text":"standards..","box":[[123,1432],[333,1432],[333,1453],[123,1453]]},{"text":"Finally an older worker told him not to do it that way, because","box":[[326,1429],[1442,1425],[1442,1452],[326,1456]]},{"text":"it was aqainst the rules.","box":[[121,1465],[564,1465],[564,1489],[121,1489]]},{"text":"So the young guy stopped because he knew he","box":[[592,1463],[1355,1459],[1355,1489],[592,1493]]},{"text":"would be criticized in a meeting if the word got out.","box":[[118,1499],[1053,1498],[1053,1525],[118,1526]]},{"text":"Workers often finished their work early and did their own personal","box":[[189,1535],[1352,1532],[1352,1559],[189,1562]]},{"text":"things.","box":[[123,1572],[246,1574],[246,1598],[123,1596]]},{"text":"This was the biggest problem with China's factories in the l970s,","box":[[278,1569],[1422,1565],[1422,1596],[278,1600]]},{"text":"indeed since 1967.","box":[[121,1606],[459,1607],[459,1631],[121,1630]]},{"text":"The discipline of workers was not as good as before","box":[[471,1605],[1373,1603],[1373,1630],[471,1632]]},{"text":"1967.","box":[[121,1643],[223,1643],[223,1667],[121,1667]]},{"text":"Before then, workers","box":[[241,1643],[601,1643],[601,1667],[241,1667]]},{"text":"scould leave their work post for a few minutes","box":[[587,1640],[1406,1638],[1406,1665],[587,1667]]},{"text":"for a drink, and rest periods were set by law, and were short.","box":[[121,1676],[1217,1674],[1217,1701],[121,1703]]},{"text":"After","box":[[1247,1674],[1338,1676],[1337,1700],[1246,1698]]},{"text":"1967, workers in his factory, when they completed a number of articles","box":[[121,1713],[1354,1709],[1354,1736],[121,1740]]},{"text":"and piled them up beside their machines, the worker would leave as long","box":[[121,1746],[1373,1744],[1373,1775],[121,1777]]},{"text":"as it did not disrupt the order of work dowm the line.","box":[[121,1784],[1113,1780],[1113,1807],[121,1811]]},{"text":"It was not like","box":[[1106,1783],[1372,1783],[1372,1807],[1106,1807]]},{"text":"electronics production lines in Hong Kong where the speed is set by a","box":[[120,1817],[1341,1815],[1342,1845],[120,1847]]},{"text":"conveyor belt.","box":[[121,1858],[367,1853],[368,1879],[121,1884]]},{"text":"Whentheir pieces","box":[[404,1856],[708,1856],[708,1879],[404,1879]]},{"text":"s piled up, they could leave for a while.","box":[[694,1853],[1404,1851],[1404,1878],[694,1880]]},{"text":"Before the CR, workers could also leave for short periods, but they did","box":[[118,1889],[1375,1886],[1375,1916],[118,1919]]},{"text":"not want to because they had a bonus system and would be paid more the","box":[[119,1927],[1357,1923],[1357,1950],[119,1953]]},{"text":"more they turned out.","box":[[119,1962],[487,1960],[488,1987],[119,1989]]},{"text":"What kinds of thingsdid workers","box":[[191,1997],[760,1996],[760,2021],[191,2022]]},{"text":"dowhentheylefttheirworkposts?","box":[[748,1997],[1390,1997],[1390,2020],[748,2020]]},{"text":"They would wash their clothes with factory soap","box":[[120,2032],[956,2030],[956,2060],[120,2062]]},{"text":"0 and water, would go find","box":[[941,2033],[1391,2031],[1391,2055],[941,2057]]},{"text":"another friend in another shop and talk for 30 minutes to an hour.A","box":[[122,2069],[1330,2066],[1330,2094],[122,2097]]},{"text":"AlsO","box":[[1317,2068],[1389,2070],[1389,2092],[1316,2090]]},{"text":"they would go to the collective showers in the factory, clean up, go to","box":[[121,2104],[1374,2101],[1374,2131],[121,2134]]},{"text":"-3-","box":[[720,2153],[774,2153],[774,2180],[720,2180]]}],"dimensions":{"height":2204,"width":1557}}